Here is the code that I am currently using, some of it was from a template
```{% set popular_1 = blog_popular_posts('1', 6) %}
    {% set popular_2 = blog_popular_posts('2', 6) %}
    {% set popular_3 = blog_popular_posts('3', 6) %}
    {% set popular_4 = blog_popular_posts('4', 6) %}
    {% set popular_5 = blog_popular_posts('5', 6) %}
    {% set  pop_tags = popular_2 + popular_3 + popular_4 + popular_1 + popular_5 %}
     {# set array variable name as topics #}
      {% set topics = [] %}
        {% for pop_tag in pop_tags %} 
        {# add topic of popular posts into array variable topics #}
        {% set topics = topics + pop_tag.topic_list %}    	    	   
        {# check if it is last loop #}
          {% if loop.last %}
          {# sort topics name and filter duplicate/repeated names in array #}
          {% set topics = topics|sort(true, false, 'name')|unique('name')  %}    
            {% for topic in topics %} 
              {% if pop_tag.topic_list %}
                &lt;a class="topic-link" href="{{ blog_tag_url.slug }}/topic/{{ topic }}"&gt; {{ topic }} &lt;/a&gt;
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}```

But blog_tag_url isnâ€™t pulling the correct information
